    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"\"\npage-layout: full\ntoc: true\ntoc-depth: 2\nexecute:\n  echo: false\n  warning: false\n  message: false\n---\n\n```{=html}\n<!-- PAGE HERO -->\n<section class=\"page-banner\">\n  <div style=\"max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n    <h1>Country Health Facilities Data</h1>\n    <p>Select a country below to explore and download facility datasets</p>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- COUNTRY SELECTOR -->\n<section style=\"max-width: 1200px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0 2rem;\">\n  <div class=\"card-modern\" style=\"border-top: 4px solid var(--map-red, #c9a227);\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Select a Country</h3>\n    <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 1rem; align-items: end;\">\n      <div>\n        <label for=\"country-select\" style=\"display: block; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\">Choose a country:</label>\n        <select id=\"country-select\" style=\"width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem;\">\n          <option value=\"\">-- Select a Country --</option>\n          <option value=\"kenya\">🇰🇪 Kenya</option>\n          <option value=\"tanzania\">🇹🇿 Tanzania</option>\n          <option value=\"uganda\">🇺🇬 Uganda</option>\n          <option value=\"zambia\">🇿🇲 Zambia</option>\n          <option value=\"malawi\">🇲🇼 Malawi</option>\n          <option value=\"nigeria\">🇳🇬 Nigeria</option>\n          <option value=\"benin\">🇧🇯 Benin</option>\n        </select>\n      </div>\n      <button id=\"load-map-btn\" class=\"btn-primary\" style=\"margin: 0;\">Load Map & Data</button>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n```\n\n## Interactive Facility Map\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"leaflet html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-fcd043d4fdfcb1bcfcce\" style=\"width:100%;height:464px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-fcd043d4fdfcb1bcfcce\">{\"x\":{\"options\":{\"crs\":{\