n\" style=\"border-top: 4px solid var(--map-red, #c9a227);\">\n      <h3 style=\"margin-top: 0; color: var(--map-red, #c9a227);\">🗺️ Download GeoJSON</h3>\n      <p style=\"color: #666;\">Get facility data in GeoJSON format with full geographic properties. Ideal for web mapping and GIS analysis.</p>\n      <button class=\"btn-cta\" style=\"width: 100%;\">Download Kenya Facilities (GeoJSON)</button>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 0.85rem; color: #999; margin-top: 1rem;\">Last updated: 2026-05-01 | Format: GeoJSON</p>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 2rem; padding: 1.5rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201, 162, 39, 0.05) 0%, rgba(201, 162, 39, 0.02) 100%); border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid rgba(201, 162, 39, 0.2);\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666;\">\n      <strong>License:</strong> All data released under <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: var(--map-red, #c9a227); text-decoration: none;\">CC BY 4.0</a> license. \n      You are free to use, share, and adapt with attribution. <strong>Version 1.2.1</strong> • Dataset ID: <code style=\"background: white; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">KEN-HF-2026-01</code>\n    </p>\n  </div>\n\n</section>\n```\n\n## Facilities Summary Table\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"datatables html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-29195da2d9d56dc4d390\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-29195da2d9d56dc4d390\">{\"x\":{\"filter\":\"top\",\"vertical\":false,\"filterHTML\":\"<tr>\\n  <td><\\/td>\\n  <td data-type=\\\"character\\\" style=\\\"vertical-align: top;\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"form-group has-feedback\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom: auto;\\\">\\n      <input type=\\\"search\\\" placeholder=\\\"All\\\" class=\\\"form-control\\\" style=\\\"width: 100%;\\\"/>\\n      <span class=\\\"glyphicon glyphicon-remove-circ